Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}在如空壳般的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}何を見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}目覚めた理由ですら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.28,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}就连醒来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}也都还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:47.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}信じることに酷く怯えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:47.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}非常害怕「相信别人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}だって 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}因为 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}捨てたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}都已经舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:58.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}こんな世界ならもう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:58.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}这样的世界 干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}消えてしまえと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}消失不见就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}憎んでいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}曾经憎恶的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}張り裂けそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}像是要裂开一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}即使我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:19.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}ほら キミの声が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:19.59,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}看 你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}僕を救うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:29.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}何度も呼び覚ますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:29.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}唤醒了我无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:34.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}キミが教えてくれた想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:34.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}你教给我的这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:37.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}そう 何度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:37.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}然后我也会 无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:43.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}キミの名前を叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:43.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}都呼喊着你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}強くその手を握って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:47.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}用力握紧你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}もう離さない決して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.73,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}绝对不会再松手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}どんな未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}无论未来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:57.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}キミとなら逃げない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:57.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}与你一起的话都不会再逃避
Comment: 0,0:22:57.88,0:22:59.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,----------------------------ED END------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,矿石卖了不少钱 这些你都可以随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:04.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:07.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:08.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:10.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:16.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我们绝对要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:21.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:30.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,果然儿童套餐 还是要这样才对啊
